<% layout('layouts/boilerplate')%>
<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid servicesJumbo">
	<div class="overlay"></div>
	<div class="container align-items-center">
		<h1 class="display-4">SERVICES</h1>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="container">
	<div class="card">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-12">
				<img class="cardImg" src="/P3.1.groupwalks.jpg" alt="" />
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-7 col-sm-12 mt-3 mainServ">
				<h4>Group Walks</h4>
				<ul class="mt-3 offset-1">
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>Group Walks are 90 minutes</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>Pick up by 10am and drop off by 1pm latest</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList"><p>Max 6 dogs per walk</p></li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					These are fun walks in local park. These can be on or off
					lead. Dogs do need to be fit, social and have a good re-call
					if they are off lead.
				</p>
				<p><b>£15 per walk </b></p>
				<p>(2nd dog £7 if they are from the same home)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="card mt-5">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-12">
				<img class="cardImg" src="/P3.2solowalks.jpg" alt="" />
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-7 col-sm-12 mt-3 mainServ">
				<h4>Solo Walks</h4>
				<ul class="mt-3 offset-1">
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>
							Solo Walks are 90 minutes (including pick up and
							drop off)
						</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>Afternoon time slots to meet your needs</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					These walks are perfect for dogs that prefer their own space
					and can be reactive or if you are working on anything in
					particular and would prefer your dogs to be walked alone.
				</p>
				<p><b>£25 per walk </b></p>
				<p>(Afternoons only)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="card mt-5">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-12">
				<img class="cardImg" src="/P3.3solowalks1hr.jpg" alt="" />
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-7 col-sm-12 mt-3 mainServ">
				<h4>Short Solo Walks</h4>
				<ul class="mt-3 offset-1">
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>
							Short Solo Walks are 30 minutes (including pick up
							and drop off)
						</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>Afternoon time slots to meet your needs</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					These walks are great for dogs that are - very young, older,
					recovering from injury, or dogs that only need a short
					afternoon walk.
				</p>
				<p><b>£15 per walk </b></p>
				<p>(Afternoons only)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="card mt-5">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-lg-5 col-sm-12">
				<img class="cardImg" src="/P3.4.daycare.jpg" alt="" />
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-7 col-sm-12 mt-3 mainServ">
				<h4>Daycare</h4>
				<ul class="mt-3 offset-1">
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>
							Day Care collection between 9am -10am, drop off at
							5pm
						</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>Day care is ran from our home</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>90 minutes walk in the morning</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>Shorter walk in the afternoon</p>
					</li>
					<li class="serviceList">
						<p>
							Numbers are kept low to make sure that there is
							enough sofa room and snuggle time to go round.
						</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					Our day care is aimed at dogs that enjoy relaxing as well as
					fun and are looking for a home from home. While dogs are
					with us they are treated as part of the family. Our highest
					priority is that they feel safe, happy and comfortable in
					our home.
				</p>
				<p><strong>£30 a day </strong></p>
				<p>(2nd dog £20 if they are from the same home)</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class="mt-5">
		*** We are based in Homerton E9, if you would like your dog/dogs
		collecting and or dropping off you must be within 3 miles. ***
	</p>
</div>
